OL,3,CMarks & Spencer annual profits hit by
OL,4,Ccyber attack
OL,6,FMarks & Spencer's annual profits
OL,7,Fslumped after a major cyber attack
OL,8,Fdisrupted online sales and supply
OL,9,Fchains across the business.
OL,11,FThe retailer said on Wednesday that
OL,12,Fadjusted pre-tax profits dropped 23.8%
OL,13,Fto #671.4 million for the year to 29
OL,14,FMarch, while revenue fell to #13.8
OL,15,Fbillion.
OL,17,FDespite the disruption, the company
OL,18,Fsaid it had emerged from the year
OL,19,F"stronger" and expected to return to
OL,20,Fgrowth in the current financial year.
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
