OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779279069
OL,3,CMarks & Spencer annual profits hit by
OL,4,Ccyber attack
OL,6,FM&S was forced to suspend all online
OL,7,Fsales for around six weeks and faced
OL,8,Fempty shelves after hackers targeted
OL,9,Fits logistics systems over the Easter
OL,10,Fweekend last year. At the time, it was
OL,11,Festimated that the retailer was losing
OL,12,Faround #3.5 million for every day its
OL,13,Fwebsite remained offline.
OL,15,FThe attack was one of several major
OL,16,Fhacks to big-name British businesses
OL,17,Flast year, including Jaguar Land Rover
OL,18,Fand the Co-op.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
