OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779279069
OL,3,CMarks & Spencer annual profits hit by
OL,4,Ccyber attack
OL,6,FThe retailer also pushed ahead with
OL,7,Fits major transformation plan, with
OL,8,Fincluded the opening 12 new food
OL,9,Fstores and three full-line stores
OL,10,Foffering food and clothing.
OL,12,FChief executive Stuart Machin said the
OL,13,Fgroup was "unshaken by short-term
OL,14,Fevents" and was making progress
OL,15,Fdespite "a triple whammy of
OL,16,Fheadwinds", including the Iran war,
OL,17,Fincreased taxation and tighter
OL,18,Fregulations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
