OL,3,CMarks & Spencer annual profits hit by
OL,4,Ccyber attack
OL,6,F"We have a clear plan and there is
OL,7,Fmuch within our control as we reinvest
OL,8,Fin value and quality for our
OL,9,Fcustomers," he said.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FThe group's fashion, home and beauty
OL,17,Foperations were particularly badly
OL,18,Faffected by the hack, with online
OL,19,Fsales suspended, stock flow disrupted
OL,20,Fand availability restricted by the
OL,21,Fcyber attack.
