OL,3,CMarks & Spencer annual profits hit by
OL,4,Ccyber attack
OL,6,FSales in the division fell by 7.7%
OL,7,Fover the past year as a result. In
OL,8,Fcontrast, the group's food arm
OL,9,Freported 7% sales growth for the year.
OL,11,FMachine said: "That was an
OL,12,Fextraordinary year. We were laser-
OL,13,Ffocused on our customers, worked
OL,14,Fincredibly hard to recover our
OL,15,Fbusiness, and we came out stronger.
OL,26,@sD@OOU
