OL,3,CMarks & Spencer annual profits hit by
OL,4,Ccyber attack
OL,6,F"Throughout, we were transparent with
OL,7,Fcustomers and they rewarded us with
OL,8,Ftheir loyalty. We remain the UK's most
OL,9,Ftrusted brand, and we never take that
OL,10,Ffor granted. We aim to serve our
OL,11,Fcustomers better every day, and we
OL,12,Fthank them for shopping with us. We
OL,13,Fcontinue to invest in the value,
OL,14,Fquality and innovation that they look
OL,15,Ffor in M&S."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
