OL,6,FSpeaking at the time, Machin said the
OL,7,Fdata had been accessed due to the
OL,8,F"sophisticated nature of the incident"
OL,9,Fbut stressed that this does not
OL,10,Finclude payment or card details, or
OL,11,Faccount passwords.
